680v6 Bungee Infant Wide 'Phantom Stellar Blue'
results.story: The New Balance 680v6 Bungee Infant Wide Phantom Stellar Blue features a dark grey mesh upper secured with elastic no-tie laces and an adjustable hook-and-loop strap, allowing easy on and off for little feet. The ventilated build is accented with a pink and turquoise N logo and a blue leather heel overlay. The slip-on silhouette is underpinned by a soft foam midsole, offering lightweight cushioning with each step. A two-tone rubber outsole yields durable traction underfoot.

results.name: 680v6 Bungee Infant 'Phantom Stellar Blue'
results.story: The New Balance 680v6 Bungee Infant Phantom Stellar Blue features running-inspired cushioning, highlighted by a stacked foam midsole with a durable rubber outsole underfoot. Up top, ventilated black mesh is accented with a turquoise N logo and bolstered with synthetic leather overlays at the forefoot and heel. The slip-on silhouette is secured with an adjustable hook-and-loop strap and no-tie elastic laces, which allow little feet to get dressed quickly and easily.
